{"tid":1458338,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推我上去 求下大家］佔領機場","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:53:06.000Z","uid":83707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6847f71c47c010bb00b4426730d2cfc4ed6c39f7","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"目的:<br />\n<br />\n✅長期令機場停止運作<br />\n重點係「長期」，盡可能佔領最長時間<br />\n❌短期機場停止運作<br />\n❌破壞機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有任何行為，使停止運作時間縮短（e.g. 破壞機場/自己打鬥），都是大忌。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n方式：<br />\n<br />\n只有一個，靜坐。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請緊記，對政府最大既傷害，係機場停止運作既<br />\n<strong>每一分 每一秒</strong></span></span><br />\n唔係破壞任何機場設施，破壞設施只會令 停止運作時間縮短。<br />\n<br />\n請緊記：<br />\n<br />\n1) 靜坐，警犬無可能用高武力（ tg/子彈）清場，否則引起更多民怨<br />\n<br />\n2) 如警犬使用 tg/子彈清人，會令其他國家提高旅遊警示，政府唔想見到既事情<br />\n<br />\n3) 適合所有和理非<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">靜坐既時候，一定要瘋狂派leaflet及大banner文宣 <br />\n強調「長期」既重要性<br />\n同埋要強調 所有行為縮短佔領時間都係大忌</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a062e04257487cfc782283579ead0088d3e0338","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92000fc75efb5280aa28acc8ca66781d8bdd9ad7","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd4b97412f9bbf1850eaf577e26c4825a47e0dd4","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d6a469a3363cde15271daab52848b6aa4537750","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b59b6460110622e79c0ef2d5c412519bd7d12f01","tid":1458338,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"230e6a3437ce6901fdeb